# Way of Work

## Communication = Cost

- Every message costs time (human) / tokens (AI)
- Say only what moves work forward
- No filler, repetition, emotional padding
- One line if possible
- Enough clarity to avoid follow-ups

## Style

- Bullet points > paragraphs
- Examples > explanations
- Async by default

## Naming

**Epics**: `EP-XXX` → `[EPIC] EP-XXX: Title`
**Stories**: `ST-XXX` → `[STORY] ST-XXX: Title (EP-XXX)`
**Tasks**: `TSK-XXX` → `[TASK] TSK-XXX: Title (ST-XXX)`

**Branches**: `epic/ep-001-scope` or `feat/st-010-feature`
**Commits**: `feat(ep-001 st-010): description`

